high_descs: Turn around, go across the room and then turn right to the white table.
Pick up the knife in front of the tomato.
Cut the tomato on the back of the table.
Turn to the right and then turn back to the left to the white table.
Put the knife on the table across the top of the other knife.
Look up at the tomato on the back of the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn right and head to the stove.
Put the slice of tomato in the right pan.
Pick up the right pan with the tomato in it.
Turn around and go across the room to the black table.
Put the pan in the middle of the table behind the pot.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a slice of tomato in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn right at the white rectangular table, go to the table.
Take the large knife pointing towards the bowl and salt on the table.
Cut the left tomato on the table into slices.
Move backwards a step from the table, face the table.
Put the knife on the table.
Move forward to the table.
Take a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn around, go forward, turn left and go forward to the oven.
Put the tomato in the pan on the right of the stove top.
Take the right pan from the stove top.
Turn around, go forward, turn left at the round black table.
Put the pan behind the pot on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a tomato in it on a table.

high_descs: Go to the white table
Pick up the farther knife
Cut the farther tomato
Turn and look at the white table
Put the knife down
Look up at the tomato
Pick up a tomato slice
Go to the stove
Put the tomato on a pan
Pick up the pan
Go to the black table
Put the pan down on the black table
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a tomato slice down on a table
